- **Abusive Behavior**: Any harassment, cyber-attacks, or unethical use of the data patterns.

**LEGAL WARNING**: Unauthorized access or malicious intent directed at this infrastructure is a federal offense under national cyber laws. Given its institutional affiliation, UniZ maintains a zero-tolerance policy. **Any abusive behavior or criminal exploitation will result in prosecution to the fullest extent of the law, which may include heavy fines, permanent academic expulsion, and imprisonment.**

